Heat oven to 425 degrees F. Place 3/4 cup BUSH'S BEST Kidney Beans in small bowl and partially mash with potato masher or back of wooden spoon. Add salsa; mix well. Spread mixture evenly over pizza crust. Top pizza with cheese, remaining beans, peppers and onions. Place pizza on baking sheet; bake for 12 minutes or until cheese is melted and crust is golden brown. Top with cilantro; cut into 12 thin wedges. Serve warm.